# Task 14 – Access Control for Borrow Request Table

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task configures Access Control Lists (ACLs) for the Borrow Request table to implement role-based permissions.

## ACL Configuration

### Create
- Student

### Read
- Student
- Librarian

### Write
- Librarian

### Delete
- Librarian

## Testing

- Verified Student can create borrow requests.
- Verified Student can read borrow requests.
- Verified Student cannot update or delete requests.
- Verified Librarian can read, update, and delete requests.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- Access Control Lists (ACL)
- Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

## Status

Completed
